section.section:
"Vehicle" means, except as otherwise provided in this subsection, any vehicle registered or to be registered in this State as:
A Class A (passenger) vehicle;
A Class M (multipurpose) vehicle;
A Class J (vanpool) vehicle;
A Class E (truck) vehicle;
A Class F (tractor) vehicle;
A Class G (trailer) vehicle;
A Class B (for-hire) vehicle; or
A Class D (motorcycle) vehicle.
